dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Plates VII and VIII from: Black's general atlas : comprehending sixty-one maps from the latest and most authentic sources / engraved on steel ... by Sydney Hall, Hughes,&c ... Edinburgh : Adam and Charles Black, 1854. Inset: Scilly Isles. Shows actual and proposed railway lines.
